name: ComplimentKetchup
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: compliment ketchup
des:
Ask Alexa for "Compliment Ketchup" to get one of over 50 different compliments to brighten your day. If you didn't quite catch the compliment, or want to hear one again, tell Alexa to "repeat", or ask "what was that?"

These compliments are designed to give you a momentary break from your stressful day and make you smile; so next time you're feeling down and out, try asking Alexa for some "compliment ketchup" and see if you don't feel a little bit better!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
